#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.cov.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.cov"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:1 of
msgid "Compute covariance with Series, excluding missing values."
msgstr "计算与 Series 的协方差，排除缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:3 of
msgid ""
"The two `Series` objects are not required to be the same length and will "
"be aligned internally before the covariance is calculated."
msgstr "两个 `Series` 对象不需要长度相同，在计算协方差之前会进行内部对齐。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:6 of
msgid "Series with which to compute the covariance."
msgstr "用于计算协方差的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:8 of
msgid "Minimum number of observations needed to have a valid result."
msgstr "获得有效结果所需的最小观测数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:10 of
msgid ""
"Delta degrees of freedom.  The divisor used in calculations is ``N - "
"ddof``, where ``N`` represents the number of elements."
msgstr "自由度调整。计算中使用的除数是 ``N - ddof``，其中 ``N`` 表示元素数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:14 of
msgid ""
"Covariance between Series and other normalized by N-1 (unbiased "
"estimator)."
msgstr "Series 与其他数据之间按 N-1 归一化的协方差（无偏估计）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:21 of
msgid "Compute pairwise covariance of columns."
msgstr "计算列之间的成对协方差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reduction.cov.cov_series:24 of
msgid "示例"
